							"type": "paragraph",
							"attrs": {
								"dir": "auto"
							},
							"content": [
								{
									"type": "text",
									"text": "Nammude project-il real-time notifications build cheyyan vendi nadanna aah oru 'epic' journey-ude documentation aanu ithu. End-to-end flow connect cheyyan kurachu 'Bottlenecks' undayirunnu, pakshe nammal athu ellam onnonnayi solve cheythu."
