											"content": [
												{
													"type": "text",
													"marks": [
														{
															"type": "bold"
														}
													],
													"text": "Problem"
												},
												{
													"type": "text",
													"text": ": Backend-il JWT "
												},
												{
													"type": "text",
													"marks": [
														{
															"type": "code"
														}
													],
													"text": "HttpOnly=True"
												},
												{
													"type": "text",
													"text": " aayirunnu. Athukondu Frontend-il Javascript-inu access_token 'read' cheyyan pattillayirunnu. Nammal aadyam token URL parameter vazhi ayakkan nokki, pakshe JS-inu token edukkan pattathathu kondu connection connect aayilla."
